        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "A ruler — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Of the people, or a civil magistrate. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Where they kill the burnt-offering — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "So called by way of eminence, to wit, the daily burnt-offering. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "It is a sin-offering — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And therefore to be killed where the burnt-offering is killed; whereby it is distinguished from the peace- offerings, which were killed elsewhere.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
